---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro'
import MastheadBg from '../layouts/MastheadBg.astro'
import {
  IoSpeedometerOutline,
  IoCallOutline,
  IoBrushOutline,
  IoPhonePortraitOutline,
  IoMailOutline
} from 'react-icons/io5/index.js'
---

<!-- bio -->
<MastheadBg>
  <PageLayout transparentNav={true}>
    <section class="md:py-28 overflow-hidden text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="mx-auto">
          <h1
            class="mb-6 font-heading text-center text-white text-4xl md:text-7xl xl:text-10xl font-bold"
          >
            About Us
          </h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col p-6 md:p-28 space-y-8 md:space-y-0">
          <div class="mx-auto w-1/2 md:w-1/3">
            <img
              src="pfp.jpg"
              alt="Nicholas E."
              class="rounded-full shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-8 mx-auto">
            <p
              class="font-heading text-black text-sm md:text-md xl:text-lg font-light"
            >
              Queen City Design
            </p>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-black text-5xl font-bold">
              Giving Small Businesses The Big Business Treatment
            </h2>
            <p class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-800">
              Hi there - I'm Nicholas, owner and sole developer of Queen City
              Design.
              <br />
              <br />
              I started programming after achieving success in the electronic sports
              industry by working for <a
                href="https://www.blizzard.com/en-us/company/about"
                class="text-fuchsia-500 underline">Blizzard Entertainment</a
              > - a Fortune 100 company. Later, I wanted a career more aligned with
              my personal values and entrepreneurial ambition.
              <br />
              <br />
              In only a year, I taught myself to build websites and applications
              that solve real-world business problems which landed me positions at
              large tech companies with considerable responsbility.
              <br />
              <br />
              Over a few years of work, I was solving real problems for real businesses
              - and seeing the lucrative growth they achieved afterwards. And by
              doing so, I discovered a problem for many small businesses: <strong
                >They don't have the funds to drop thousands of dollars upfront
                on a new website</strong
              >
              - making it difficult to compete with the big players in their industries.
              <br />
              <br />
              And the ones that did... got taken advantage of. They were given terrible
              websites which looked pieced together by someone in a dungeon who hasn't
              seen design trends for the past decade. Worst of all, the website never
              focused on solving the underlying problem of <span class="italic"
                >why</span
              > they needed a website in the first place (to grow their business)!
              <br />
              <br />
              What a waste.
              <br />
              <br />
              In addition, shady web developers made clients responsible for dealing
              with their own hosting service, content backups, website edits, general
              maintanence, SEO optimization and so on... unless they shelled out
              even more money.
              <br />
              <br />
              Frustrating, right?
              <br />
              <br />
              Many small businesses either can't afford a quality website, and if
              they can, they don't know who to trust to make something great without
              putting even more responsibility on themselves. Isn't the point of
              hiring someone that they solve your problem from start to finish?
              <br />
              <br />
              <strong
                >So I built a business model to fit their needs: The $0 down and
                $199 a month model.</strong
              > It's managable for a small business's bank account and comes with
              the peace of mind they'll have a strong, revenue-generating web presence
              to get them closer to their #1 goal: Growing their business.
              <br />
              <br />
              Excited to level up your business's web presence? <a
                href="/contact"
                class="text-fuchsia-500 underline"
                >Reach out now to set up a free consultation.</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- TODO: feature section -->
    <section class="pt-28 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <p
          class="mb-5 font-heading font-semibold text-xs text-gray-400 text-center uppercase tracking-px"
        >
          Business-first approach
        </p>
        <h2
          class="mb-20 font-heading font-semibold text-6xl sm:text-7xl text-gray-900 text-center"
        >
          <span class="bg-gradient-cyan text-transparent bg-clip-text"
            >Quality</span
          > over Quantity
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-4">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-4">
            <div class="md:max-w-xs mx-auto text-center space-y-4">
              <IoSpeedometerOutline className="text-5xl text-black w-full" />
              <p class="font-heading font-medium text-xl text-gray-900">
                SEO-First Code
              </p>
              <p class="font-heading text-lg text-gray-800">
                Blazing fast sites by default. We hand-build each website to
                outrank your competition.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-4">
            <div class="md:max-w-xs mx-auto text-center space-y-4">
              <IoCallOutline className="text-5xl text-black w-full" />
              <p class="font-heading font-medium text-xl text-gray-900">
                Unbeatable Customer Service
              </p>
              <p class="font-heading text-lg text-gray-800">
                No automated systems - when you need help, the lead developer
                answers your call.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-4">
            <div class="md:max-w-xs mx-auto text-center space-y-4">
              <IoBrushOutline className="text-5xl text-black w-full" />
              <p class="font-heading font-medium text-xl text-gray-900">
                Limitless Design
              </p>
              <p class="font-heading text-lg text-gray-800">
                We can edit our designs to cater to your tastes. Everything is
                customizable!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section
      class="pt-28 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-white px-4 flex flex-wrap space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-8 justify-center"
    >
      <div class="flex space-x-4 justify-center">
        <div class="w-16">
          <IoPhonePortraitOutline className="text-5xl text-black" />
        </div>
        <span class="h-12 border-r border-black"></span>
        <div class="w-32 md:w-full">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl text-black">Phone:</h3>
          <a
            href="tel:+1-336-523-8016"
            class="font-heading underline text-fuchsia-500"
          >
            (336) 523-8016
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex space-x-4 justify-center">
        <div class="w-16">
          <IoMailOutline className="text-5xl text-black" />
        </div>
        <span class="h-12 border-r border-black"></span>
        <div class="w-32 md:w-full">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl text-black">Email:</h3>
          <a
            href="mailto:nicholas@qc-design.com"
            class="font-heading underline text-fuchsia-500 whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            nicholas@qc-design.com
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="relative pt-28 pb-20 bg-gradient-gray overflow-hidden">
      <img
        class="absolute top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 left-0"
        src="gradia-assets/elements/sign-up/radial.svg"
        alt=""
      />
      <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-6 justify-center">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-6">
            <div class="md:max-w-xl">
              <h2
                class="mb-12 font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 text-6xl sm:text-7xl"
              >
                Let's Start Building
              </h2>
              <!-- <p class="mb-12 text-lg text-gray-500">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
                Malesuada tellus vestibulum, commodo pulvinar.
              </p> -->
              <form
                name="contact"
                method="POST"
                data-netlify="true"
                data-netlify-recaptcha="true"
              >
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-2 mb-6">
                  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-2">
                    <input
                      class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 text-gray-500 placeholder-gray-500 bg-white outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg"
                      type="text"
                      placeholder="First name"
                      name="first-name"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-2">
                    <input
                      class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 text-gray-500 placeholder-gray-500 bg-white outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg"
                      type="text"
                      placeholder="Last name"
                      name="last-name"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full p-2">
                    <input
                      class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 text-gray-500 placeholder-gray-500 bg-white outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg"
                      type="text"
                      placeholder="Email address"
                      name="email"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full p-2">
                    <textarea
                      class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 text-gray-500 placeholder-gray-500 bg-white outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg"
                      placeholder="Tell us about your project..."
                      name="message"
                      cols="30"
                      rows="10"></textarea>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-1.5 mb-8">
                  <div class="w-auto p-1.5" data-netlify-recaptcha="true"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:max-w-max">
                  <button
                    type="submit"
                    class="w-full font-heading font-semibold text-xs text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-px overflow-hidden rounded-md hover:ring-2 hover:ring-green-300 hover:ring-opacity-50"
                  >
                    <div
                      class="relative p-5 px-9 bg-gradient-green overflow-hidden rounded-md"
                    >
                      <p class="relative z-10">Contact Us</p>
                    </div>
                  </button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </PageLayout>
</MastheadBg>
